Class D3Code

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cloudofficeprint.RenderElements.RenderElement

  • public class D3Code
extends Property
    With Word/Excel/PowerPoint documents, it's possible to let Cloud Office Print execute some JavaScript code to generate a D3 image (Data Driven Documents).
